                            "termSource": null,
                            "termAccession": ""
                        },
                        "description": "<p>1 ml of each collected sample was centrifuged (30 s at max speed) and 450 \u00b5l of supernatant was used for metabolite extraction. The remainder of the samples was frozen at -80 \u00b0C as backup.</p>",
